Package com.googlecode.prmf.merapi.net.event

Network event classes.

See:
          Description

Interface Summary
NetworkEvent Object representation of a network event.
NetworkEventListener An object that reacts to network events.
 

Class Summary
AbstractNetworkEvent A basic NetworkEvent implementation.
AbstractNetworkEventListener A stub NetworkEventListener.
ConnectedEvent Raised when a connection is successfully completed.
DisconnectedEvent Raised when a socket disconnects or when a connection times out.
MessageEvent A NetworkEvent that comes with a message!
ReadingEvent Raised when an incoming message is successfully read.
WritingEvent Raised when an outgoing message is written to a socket.
